{"tid":815293,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個女仔，我入了一間全部都係男人嘅公司","createTime":"2018-09-12T03:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T00:46:27.000Z","uid":10277,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70bde83b0a46d2d41343da848eb6353e992aa81e","tid":815293,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"我20+歲<br />\n入面平均年齡30-40+<br />\n<br />\n我-中下樣 唔肥唔高<br />\n<br />\n做錯野永遠唔會俾人鬧<br />\n終於明白點解社會成日女人可以拿塊西出黎嘟<br />\n因為啲男人係唔知點解係會讓你忍你<br />\n<br />\n除左一啲比較八婆性格有啲女人嘅男同事唔妥我之外 成日打我小報告都無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為老細都已經五、六十歲 當我孫女咁款<br />\n整體工作都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671a9445205ed1d9f119a8c7591a8123b4a3cada","tid":815293,"uid":190564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"咩公司?做咩架?"},{"pid":"df9ce427556575fb9d1fde1e7cd5d14029abb7d8","tid":815293,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"671a9445205ed1d9f119a8c7591a8123b4a3cada","tid":815293,"uid":190564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"咩公司?做咩架?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:04:16.000Z","msg":"外資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大品牌"},{"pid":"f013a3afbcaa7c010cc12b400719e9154af45a2d","tid":815293,"uid":16530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"卡樂b?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71259de46b95f8e1bad1e74d9e2e595bc2992e73","tid":815293,"uid":165368,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"中下樣=男同事當你路人"},{"pid":"81e9e9b9d144e13f84a1937275ca2a7768e9dc9e","tid":815293,"uid":179562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"講真，一個中年男人鬧個後生女，佢地都覺得無面同尷尬啦"}